title: Boligjakten
overview: The real estate agents, Karianne Amlie and Hans Christian Espenes, will once again help people to claw at the dream home. Buying a home is an important choice of life and probably the biggest investment you make. Should you move from the city, buy a home for the first time or move from a detached house to an apartment? Our experts help ordinary people find the dream home in their local area. In each episode, we join couples, families and singles on different shows in search of their new home. In addition, viewers receive tips and advice from the experts on what to look for when looking for a new home, as well as how to win a bidding round.
